BT /F1 6.3 Tf 60.00 288.00 Td (1. TV: 2x 55" - DIMENSIONS 1230 x 710 x 60 MM ARE AN ESTIMATE OF A TYPICAL MODEL, CONFIRM AGAINST THE FINAL TV TYPE. CENTRE HEIGHT 1850 MM, BOTTOM EDGE 1495 MM (CLEARS MINI ARENA RAILING 1200 MM), TOP EDGE 2205 MM < GRAPHIC AREA 2474 MM.) Tj ET
BT /F1 6.3 Tf 60.00 277.50 Td (2. EACH TV AND THE PRESENTER BOX MUST BE CENTRED ON A PANEL CENTRE - VESA / WALL MOUNT WITHIN A SINGLE 986 MM PANEL MODULE, NEVER ACROSS A JOINT. PANEL LOAD CAPACITY = OPEN QUESTION AT GES, DO NOT INSTALL BEFORE CONFIRMATION.) Tj ET
BT /F1 6.3 Tf 60.00 267.00 Td (3. * WALL B LENGTH 5940 MM IS AN ASSUMPTION (2 x 2970); PANEL COUNT AND SPACING TO BE CONFIRMED BY GES. TV POSITIONS ARE DEFINED BY PANEL CENTRES (P2, P4), NOT BY ABSOLUTE X - RE-CHECK AFTER GES CONFIRMATION.) Tj ET
BT /F1 6.3 Tf 60.00 256.50 Td (4. PRESENTER: WHITE BOX 600 x 1040 x 80 MM WITH 3x 27" SCREENS 600 x 337.5 MM STACKED (GAPS ~6.9 MM). CENTRE HEIGHT 1500 MM = ESTIMATE (EYE LEVEL, NOT SPECIFIED) - BOX HANGS 980-2020 MM. GAP TO MINI EXHIBIT 186 MM.) Tj ET
BT /F1 6.3 Tf 60.00 246.00 Td (5. DASHED OUTLINES ON WALL B = EXHIBITS STANDING IN FRONT OF THE WALL (MINI TOWER H 1803 MM, ARCADE TOTEM H 1800 MM) - THEY DEFINE THE FREE ZONE FOR THE TVS. SHELL SCHEME GES AMP, WALL HEIGHT 2500 MM.) Tj ET
